                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the adamant sentinel is at 0 HP, it isn't destroyed. Instead, it enters repair mode, during which it's @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1}, can't take reactions, and can take only the Self-Repair action. Once it has more than 30 HP, it can use any type of action and can use reactions, though it remains slowed 1 and can't take any reactions until the start of its next turn. If a critical hit with a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Vorpal] adamantine weapon reduces the sentinel to 0 HP, or if such a weapon hits it while it's already at 0 HP, the sentinel is destroyed.</p>"
